RawLine: QINFO_10023,據說五毒血術可能藏在藥王密窖內，調查藥王遺蹟各處，找出密窖吧。此類密窖多藏在古井、牆縫等處，也可以前往藥王大廳尋找線索。（藥王遺跡）,据说五毒血术可能藏在药王密窖内，调查药王遗蹟各处，找出密窖吧。此类密窖多藏在古井、墙缝等处，也可以前往药王大厅寻找线索。（药王遗迹）

Items.mt: It is said that the Five Poison Blood Art may be hidden in the secret vaults of the Medicine King, so investigate the various parts of the Medicine King's ruins to find the secret vaults. These secret vaults are mostly hidden in ancient wells and cracks in the walls, or you can go to the Medicine King Hall to find clues. (Medicine King Ruins)
